   28,683-28,692, 1998.

   McDermid, I. S., J. B. Bergwerff, G. Bodeker, I. S. Boyd, E. J.
   Brinksma, B. J. Connor, R. Farmer, M. R. Gross, P. Kimvilakani, W. A.
   Matthews, T. J. McGee, F. T. Ormel, A. Parrish, U. Singh, D. P. J.
   Swart, and J. J. Tsou. OPAL: Network for the Detection of Stratospheric
   Change Ozone Profiler Assessment at Lauder, New Zealand. II.
   Intercomparison of Revised Results. J. Geophys. Res., 103,
   28,693-28,699, 1998.

   Boyd, I. S., Greg E. Bodeker, Brian J. Connor, Daan P.J. Swart, and
   Ellen J. Brinksma, An assessment of ECC ozonesondes operated using 1%
   and 0.5% Kl cathode solutions at Lauder, New Zealand, Geophys. Res.
   Lett., 25, 2409-2412, 1998

   Brinksma, E.J., et al., Validation of 3 years of ozone measurements
