   MLO, Hawaii, USA

   McDermid, I. S., T. J. McGee, and D. P. J. Swart, NDSC Lidar
   Intercomparisons and Validation: OPAL and MLO3 Campaigns in 1995,
   Advances in Atmospheric Remote Sensing with Lidar, Springer New
   York-Berlin-Heidelberg, 525-528, 1996.

   McPeters, R. D., D. J. Hofmann, M. Clark, L. Flynn, L. Froidevaux, M.
   Gross, B. Johnson, G. Koenig, X. Liu, I. S. McDermid, T. McGee, F.
   Murcray, M. J. Newchurch, S. Oltmans, A. Parrish, R. Schnell, U. Singh,
   J. J. Tsou., T. D. Walsh, and J. M. Zawodny, Results from the 1995
