   lidars at OHP during UARS validation campaign, J. Geophys. Res., 101,
   10287-10297, 1996.

   Braathen G.O., T.J. McGee, M.R. Gross, S. Godin, P. Keckhut, C. Vialle,
   and A. Hauchecorne, Intercomparaison of stratospheric ozone and
   temperature measurements at the Observatoire de Haute Provence during
   an NDSC validation campaign from 1-18 july 1997, To be submitted to
   Geophys. Res. Lett., 2000.

   Tsukuba, Japan

   Namboothiri, S. P. , N, Sugimoto, H. Nakane, I. Matsui and Y. Murayama,
   Rayleigh lidar observation of temperature over Tsukuba: winter thermal
   structure and comparison studies, Earth, Planets and Space, 51,
   825-832, 1999.

3. Algorithm comparisons

   Ozone

   Godin, S., A. I. Carswell, D. P. Donovan, H. Claude, W. Steinbrecht, I.
   S. McDermid, T. J. McGee, M. R. Gross, H Nakane, D. P. J. Swart, H. B.
