   absorption lidar algorithm intercomparison, Appl. Opt., 38, 6225-6236,
   1999

   Temperature

   Leblanc, T., I.S. McDermid, A. Hauchecorne and P. Keckhut, Evaluation
   of optimization of lidar temperature analysis algorithms using
   simulated data, J. Geophys. Res., 103, 6177-6187, 1998.

